   6:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_gpio.c ****   *          This file provides firmware functions to manage the following
   7:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_gpio.c ****   *          functionalities of the General Purpose Input/Output (GPIO) peripheral:
   8:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_gpio.c ****   *           + Initialization and de-initialization functions
   9:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_gpio.c ****   *           + IO operation functions
